parameters: The day I first met Aki.
akih1
Hinata Aki: 「...!」
Hinata Aki: Oh, you... It's our first time meeting, right?
souta
Sota: ...Ah, yeah.
Hinata Aki: I'm Aki Hinata. And you are?
Sota: I... Sota

Hinata Aki: So you're Sota! I always come here to play! So, when
you're free, do you want to play together?
Sota: ...Yeah!... Let's play!

The first time I met Aki in the park, I fell in love at first
sight.
Her chest, her face, her personality, everything was my type.
Hinata Aki: So, the person next to me is my childhood friend...

And yet... just because we're childhood friends, I'm always by
Aki's side...
That person: dislikes it...

The age difference and the length of our relationship are such
that I am treated like a child...

It's frustrating that I can't compete with <that person> who is
just lucky...
That's why I ended up wanting to make Aki even more mine.
Happy-looking child: Swings are definitely the most fun!

Sota's friend:
 I found a stag beetle earlier! Isn't it cool!
Calm child: Big brother, you seem unlucky.

Muddy child: I'm going to work hard and learn how to do a
backflip!
